    tmp = (wp.abs(wp.cos(v0 + 0.99)) * ((v0 + 0.01 / v2 + 0.82) * wp.sin(v1 + 0.51)))
    tmp = (((v2 + 0.49 - v1 + 0.36) + (tmp + 0.45 / tmp + 0.88)) - ((tmp + 0.72 / v2 + 0.25) + tmp))
    tmp = (v0 - tmp)
